@baseUrl = http://localhost:7080/nyc

### Neighborhoods — first page
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/items?f=json&limit=10

###

### Neighborhoods — second page
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/items?f=json&limit=10&offset=10

###

### Census blocks — first 5
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_census_blocks/items?f=json&limit=5

###

### Streets — first 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_streets/items?f=json&limit=10

###

### Subway stations — all (491 total)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_subway_stations/items?f=json&limit=500

###

### Homicides — first 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_homicides/items?f=json&limit=10

###

### Single feature by id — neighborhood 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/items/1?f=json

###

### Single feature by id — census block 100
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_census_blocks/items/100?f=json

###

### Features in WGS84 (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/items?f=json&limit=5&crs=http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/OGC/1.3/CRS84

###

### Features in Web Mercator (EPSG:3857)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/items?f=json&limit=5&crs=http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/3857

###

### Features in native UTM Zone 18N (EPSG:26918)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/items?f=json&limit=5&crs=http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/26918
